Flavors of the World
Wherever we fly around the globe, we have the enviable job
of tasting and savoring the cuisines of the world. We invite
you to share our discoveries while traveling with us.
Salad
GARDEN SALAD BOWL
Fresh Garden Greens in season tossed with crisp
colorful vegetables and garnishes ... Served
with our dressing of the day
Freshly Baked Dinner Roll
Creamery Butter
The Sweet Cougse
FROM THE PATISSERIE
We present an ever changing array of new
and different tarts such as Almond Chiffon,
Valencia Orange or our Monte Cristo Chocolate Tart
TWA's Freshly Brewed Coffee
Tea
Sanka
Milk
A Continental Breakfast
will be offered on this flight
Entrees
BARBECUED SALISBURY STEAK
An American Favorite! A grilled U.S. Choice
chopped beef steak topped with a tangy Barbecue Sauce.
Accompanied by a Baked Stuffed Potato
and Green Beans with Carrots
BAKED LASAGNA ALLA ROMA
Our Version of the Classic Pasta from Southern Italy.
A hearty meat sauce, Ricotta Cheese and Ground
Sweet Italian Sausage nested beween layers of Lasagna
Noodles... Enhanced by a delightful blend of Swiss
and Parmesan Cheese
COQ AU VIN
Braised Chicken presented in the classic manner with rich stocks,
a bouquet of herbs, spices, onions and red wine ...
We serve it with parsley potatoes and buttered green peas.
Please accept our apologies if your choice
is not available on today's flight
